---
name: draft-linkedin
description: Draft a single post for LinkedIn (3,000 char limit, professional voice)
triggers:
  - draft a linkedin post
  - write something for linkedin
  - post to linkedin only
  - professional post
  - linkedin post only
---

Read the skill file at `.postlane/commands/draft-linkedin.md`, then draft one post for LinkedIn. Output sets `platforms: ["linkedin"]` in `meta.json`.
